    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of Py</title>

    <para>Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user py</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Due to the deprecation of this package, the test suite is not maintained
      and cannot be run.
    </para>

